and maintenance of dominant state ideology in the wake of May 1968.\nAfter his tenure at Cahiers, Comolli continued his work as a director and has since published numerous works on film theory, documentary, and jazz.  He currently teaches film theory at the Universities of Paris VIII, Barcelona, Strasburg and Genève.In the spring of 2008, Comolli was invited to the Visions du réel documentary film festival in Nyon, Switzerland, where he developed his theory of documentary cinema.\n\n", "biography_author": "Wikidata", "date_of_biography": "2022-05-19T11:54:35.735190+10:00", "external_links": [{"id": 2339, "uri": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean-Louis_Comolli"}], "uuid": "927b8749-896c-4956-97b5-66c526a6cf62", "source": {"name": "Vernon", "slug": "vernon"}, "source_identifier": "31083", "external_references": [{"id": 10029, "source": {"name": "Wikidata", "slug": "wikidata"}, "source_identifier": "Q446583"}, {"id": 10030, "source": {"name": "VIAF", "slug": "viaf"}, "source_identifier": "84184126"}, {"id": 10031, "source": {"name": "LOC Auth", "slug": "loc-auth"}, "source_identifier": "n85274443"}, {"id": 10032, "source": {"name": "WorldCat", "slug": "worldcat"}, "source_identifier": "lccn-n85274443"}], "date_modified": "2025-05-22T22:41:54.677032+10:00"}, {"id": 83045, "name": "Claudio Bondi", "roles_in_work": [{"id": 3104528, "title": "L'ombre Rouge = the Red Shadow", "work_id": 115957, "role": "producer", "role_id": 1089, "is_primary": true}], "also_known_as": "", "date_of_birth": null, "date_of_death": null, "genders": [], "languages": [], "places_of_operation": [], "biography": "", "biography_author": null, "date_of_biography": null, "external_links": [], "uuid": "e42df042-bec8-495e-8881-df237465d9e8", "source": {"name": "Vernon", "slug": "vernon"}, "source_identifier": "31082", "external_references": [{"id": 42676, "source": {"name": "Wikidata", "slug": "wikidata"}, "source_identifier": "Q121079474"}], "date_modified": "2025-05-22T22:41:54.077645+10:00"}, {"id"